\id PHM - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG PHILEMON 22/3/91 Macnaughtan 
\h PAILIMONO 
\toc1 Pailimono paęž‰taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 Pailimono 
\toc3 Pailimono 
\mt1 Pailimono paęž‰taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Polo IĚ±taęž‰ Yesu Ketiso hone witolo hataęž‰ dipula polo hali IĚ± make nikaęž‰ kame Timodi dikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo dikaęž‰ e yankeke some Pailimono neke paęž‰taęž‰ wape pitopaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutupa mo nakaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mombolo haleme siosi wandaęž‰hali make nikaęž‰ anaęž‰ Apia make nikaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peawaasomaęž‰ hali Akipasi make iki paęž‰taęž‰ do wape epenaęž‰ alopaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso yaapomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make mo puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki make kinaęž‰e.   
\s1 Pailimononaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 4 Pailimono IĚ±maęž‰ yeni pu moneaaso tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki alo hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi lo halome.  
\v 5 Kutu piki hautaęž‰ mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo make kutaa mo Tekehali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao haleeki make opitolo hataęž‰ alome.  
\v 6 Kame dikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke ameĚ±leĚ± mo Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke hone wia taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halomaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ mo ya yeni pitolo ekitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ hone tulaleeki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ epeke putupaęž‰ ku halaęž‰eki paeyao handoelenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ walenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolome.  
\v 7 Aęž‰taęž‰e. Ya kameo. Nakaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homele ekimaęž‰ ya puki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke peayaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰paeyaęž‰me. Koto pele ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ puki mea tiawaaleme.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Pailimono paęž‰taęž‰ Onisimasi paa mie leekeeki  
\p
\v 8 Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke hataęž‰ pipitaęž‰ pa pua hataęž‰ dupi dupi laa lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 9 paa neke paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo ekimaęž‰ pa honke alaęž‰eki homeke pitolome. Do honke alo ekitaęž‰ IĚ± Polotaęž‰ koke hali hataęž‰ kone pa Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ e pokoeke handaa dipula mea pitaalemeke pitaęž‰ kone alome.  
\v 10 Ya Ketiso weki homeke Onisimasi paęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pulu pele ekinaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ honke alome. IĚ± do dipula pitaęž‰ kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi waloaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ haowaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Ambaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ epeke e pokaasaęž‰ weki na hayaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ neke IĚ± diki epeke tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke some halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Koto peleke ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki neke paęž‰taęž‰ ya pukimaęž‰ homoloeki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ epenaęž‰ alome.  
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tiki pu haoweke handaa dipula do pilume. Do pilu paęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ mulu pele tupaęž‰taęž‰ Onisimasimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke teke minaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo pa haenaęž‰e laa hone paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kototaęž‰ ya hone paęž‰laęž‰eki yaęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ muelenaęž‰ yeke ti wopu na lolueke. Pa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ puelenaęž‰ yeke waleke kitolo yu wia halome. Pa nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki na handeke hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pulueke.   
\p
\v 15 Onisimasimaęž‰ neke minaęž‰paęž‰lake hautaęž‰ pa nate hosikimaęž‰ homeke piaęž‰pate paa handaęž‰ mikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hoto paeyaotaęž‰ neke yaapo hao halieke.  
\v 16 Pate ame ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande pa hameke e pokeaęž‰ some tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me ametaęž‰ koto hau otaęž‰ topo pea dikaęž‰ epeke Ketiso kame talo ipulaęž‰me. Ame ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ya tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ epeke hali halaęž‰pate wetepe nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaliaęž‰ hali make nakaęž‰ Tekehali Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ kame makee hone witolo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo halipikie.   
\p
\v 17 Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰nie hone wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ mu halo pele tupaęž‰ kone pa handaęž‰ miaęž‰peke.  
\v 18 Mo wekimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ o tondiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ epeaaluekemaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰peke.  
\v 19 Ya kikimaęž‰ kone wape pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± Polomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kulueke laa do wape pitolo handaęž‰e. Paa nakaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ haleeki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mele ekinaęž‰ na alopate.  
\v 20 Pilisi IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homonotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo ya Ketiso kame hataęž‰ ya honke loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ piaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 21 Ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ do wapenaęž‰ honke alo hautaęž‰ pilipikie hone otaęž‰ witolome. Kotaęž‰ ya alo tupaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei peao pilipikie hone witolome.  
\v 22 Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupae. Ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu haleme ekinaęž‰ hombo peaaso IĚ±taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pono lelieke. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hapeke da pandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ tikitiki yao wiaęž‰peke.   
\s1 Aęž‰talo pimanu  
\p
\v 23 Ketisonaęž‰ haunaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandake dipula pilupaęž‰ hali Epaęž‰petasimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰talo pi tapaalaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Kutaa make ya e mandake pokolomaęž‰ haliweki Maka Aęž‰tisakusi Dimasi make Luku ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make aęž‰taloe alememe.   
\p
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki iki homeke homeke ameĚ±leĚ± nate paeyao u haenaęž‰e alome.   